claim.claim-text:
A dual energy CT system, comprising:
a scanning tunnel (2, 6) through which an object to be scanned enters/exits the dual energy CT system along a transporting direction;
an X-ray source (8) provided at a side of the scanning tunnel; and
a gantry (5) provided at an opposite side of the scanning tunnel;
wherein the detector device according to any one of claims 1-12 is mounted on the gantry.
